  <body dur="03:17.550">
    <div begin="00:19.070" end="03:17.550">
      <p begin="00:19.070" end="00:23.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:19.070" end="00:19.210">晚</span><span begin="00:19.310" end="00:19.770">风</span><span begin="00:19.770" end="00:19.880">里</span><span begin="00:19.990" end="00:20.510">藏</span><span begin="00:20.590" end="00:20.990">着</span><span begin="00:21.750" end="00:22.210">多</span><span begin="00:22.560" end="00:22.840">少</span><span begin="00:22.940" end="00:23.320">精</span><span begin="00:23.320" end="00:23.830">灵</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">晚風裡藏著多少精靈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How many elves are hiding in the evening wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">夜風にはどれだけの妖精が隠れているのだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤바람 속엔 얼마나 많은 요정이 숨어 있을까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Combien d'esprits se cachent dans la brise du soir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuántas hadas se esconden en la brisa nocturna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie viele Feen verbergen sich wohl in der Abendbrise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quantas fadas se escondem na brisa da noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько же эльфов прячется в вечернем ветре</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quanti spiriti si nascondono nella brezza della sera</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wan feng li cang zhe duo shao jing ling</span></p>
      <p begin="00:25.740" end="00:30.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:25.740" end="00:25.920">满</span><span begin="00:26.010" end="00:26.480">天</span><span begin="00:26.480" end="00:26.580">的</span><span begin="00:26.730" end="00:27.140">星</span><span begin="00:27.230" end="00:27.850">辰</span><span begin="00:28.440" end="00:28.980">都</span><span begin="00:29.330" end="00:29.500">被</span><span begin="00:29.650" end="00:30.020">唤</span><span begin="00:30.170" end="00:30.880">醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">滿天的星辰都被喚醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The stars filling the sky have all been awakened</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">満天の星々が目を覚ましていく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">밤하늘 가득한 별들이 모두 깨어났어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toutes les étoiles du ciel s'en trouvent éveillées</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Todas las estrellas del cielo han sido despertadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der ganze Himmel voller Sterne wird zum Leben erweckt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Todas as estrelas do firmamento foram despertadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пробудились все звезды на ночном небе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutte le stelle nel cielo si sono risvegliate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">man tian de xing chen dou bei huan xing</span></p>
      <p begin="00:32.660" end="00:37.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:32.660" end="00:32.840">白</span><span begin="00:32.900" end="00:33.120">天</span><span begin="00:33.120" end="00:33.330">那</span><span begin="00:33.480" end="00:33.910">些</span><span begin="00:33.970" end="00:34.130">流</span><span begin="00:34.260" end="00:34.750">放</span><span begin="00:34.750" end="00:34.970">的</span><span begin="00:35.130" end="00:36.890">光</span><span begin="00:36.890" end="00:37.490">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">白天那些流放的光明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Those exiled lights of the daytime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">昼間に放たれたあの光たちが</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">낮 동안 흩어져 있던 빛들이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces lumières exilées durant la journée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa luz que fue exiliada durante el día</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das ins Exil geschickte Licht des Tages</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquela luz que foi exilada durante o dia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тот свет что был изгнан днем</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quelle luci esiliate durante il giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">bai tian na xie liu fang de guang ming</span></p>
      <p begin="00:38.010" end="00:42.630" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:38.010" end="00:38.180">剪</span><span begin="00:38.240" end="00:38.370">接</span><span begin="00:38.470" end="00:38.900">成</span><span begin="00:38.900" end="00:39.030">夜</span><span begin="00:39.300" end="00:39.680">空</span><span begin="00:40.190" end="00:40.650">仰</span><span begin="00:40.650" end="00:40.960">望</span><span begin="00:40.960" end="00:41.140">的</span><span begin="00:41.280" end="00:41.690">风</span><span begin="00:41.800" end="00:42.630">景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">剪接成夜空仰望的風景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Spliced into the scenery we look up to in the night sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">見上げる夜空の風景へと紡がれる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하나로 엮여 우러러보는 밤하늘의 풍경이 되었네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Forgent le paysage nocturne que nous contemplons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se edita en el paisaje que admiramos en el cielo nocturno</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wird zu jener nächtlichen Kulisse verwoben zu der wir aufblicken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É recortada na paisagem que admiramos no céu noturno</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сплетается в пейзаж неба которым я любуюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Montate nel paesaggio che ammiro guardando il cielo notturno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">jian jie cheng ye kong yang wang de feng jing</span></p>
      <p begin="00:45.360" end="00:48.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:45.360" end="00:45.500">看</span><span begin="00:45.550" end="00:45.690">天</span><span begin="00:45.760" end="00:45.860">台</span><span begin="00:45.950" end="00:46.440">上</span><span begin="00:46.440" end="00:46.500">路</span><span begin="00:46.610" end="00:46.930">过</span><span begin="00:47.030" end="00:47.120">几</span><span begin="00:47.240" end="00:47.410">颗</span><span begin="00:47.450" end="00:47.550">流</span><span begin="00:47.640" end="00:48.160">星</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看天台上路過幾顆流星</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Watching a few shooting stars pass by over the rooftop</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">屋上を通り過ぎる幾つかの流れ星を見て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">옥상 위를 스쳐 지나가는 별똥별들을 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regarde ces étoiles filantes passer au-dessus du toit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Viendo pasar unas estrellas fugaces desde la azotea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieh wie ein paar Sternschnuppen über die Dachterrasse ziehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Olho para as estrelas cadentes passando pelo terraço</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотрю с крыши на пролетающие падающие звезды</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guarda qualche stella cadente passare sopra la terrazza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">kan tian tai shang lu guo ji ke liu xing</span></p>
      <p begin="00:48.670" end="00:51.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:48.670" end="00:48.800">说</span><span begin="00:48.860" end="00:49.020">出</span><span begin="00:49.100" end="00:49.290">口</span><span begin="00:49.320" end="00:49.530">的</span><span begin="00:49.660" end="00:49.990">誓</span><span begin="00:49.990" end="00:50.260">言</span><span begin="00:50.360" end="00:50.550">会</span><span begin="00:50.550" end="00:50.690">有</span><span begin="00:50.790" end="00:51.000">回</span><span begin="00:51.000" end="00:51.460">音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">說出口的誓言會有回音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The vows spoken out loud will have an echo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">口にした誓いは必ず響き合う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입 밖으로 꺼낸 맹세는 메아리가 되어 돌아올 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les vœux prononcés trouveront toujours un écho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las promesas pronunciadas tendrán su eco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ausgesprochene Schwüre werden ein Echo finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As promessas ditas em voz alta terão um eco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Произнесенные клятвы обязательно отзовутся эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le promesse pronunciate avranno un'eco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">shuo chu kou de shi yan hui you hui yin</span></p>
      <p begin="00:52.040" end="00:54.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:52.040" end="00:52.140">那</span><span begin="00:52.200" end="00:52.460">就</span><span begin="00:52.460" end="00:52.680">让</span><span begin="00:52.680" end="00:52.850">我</span><span begin="00:52.910" end="00:53.130">们</span><span begin="00:53.500" end="00:53.700">勇</span><span begin="00:53.700" end="00:53.940">敢</span><span begin="00:53.940" end="00:54.170">地</span><span begin="00:54.170" end="00:54.510">约</span><span begin="00:54.560" end="00:54.710">定</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那就讓我們勇敢地約定</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Then let us bravely make a promise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから勇敢に約束を交わそう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼 우리 용기 내어 약속하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors faisons courageusement notre promesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Entonces hagamos valientemente una promesa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also lass uns mutig unser Versprechen geben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então vamos fazer a nossa promessa corajosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так давай же смело дадим друг другу обещание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Allora promettiamocelo coraggiosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na jiu rang wo men yong gan de yue ding</span></p>
      <p begin="00:54.750" end="00:57.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:54.750" end="00:54.880">对</span><span begin="00:54.950" end="00:55.130">星</span><span begin="00:55.130" end="00:55.350">空</span><span begin="00:55.390" end="00:55.520">指</span><span begin="00:55.560" end="00:55.740">尖</span><span begin="00:55.800" end="00:55.890">画</span><span begin="00:55.970" end="00:56.370">出</span><span begin="00:56.420" end="00:56.500">了</span><span begin="00:56.650" end="00:56.920">心</span><span begin="00:57.070" end="00:57.710">形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對星空指尖畫出了心形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing a heart shape at the starry sky with our fingertips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星空に向かって指先でハートを描く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별 쏟아지는 하늘에 손끝으로 하트를 그리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dessinant un cœur du bout des doigts vers le ciel étoilé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dibujando un corazón con la punta de los dedos hacia el firmamento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und mit den Fingerspitzen ein Herz in den Sternenhimmel zeichnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desenhando um coração com a ponta dos dedos para o céu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рисуя пальцами сердце на фоне звездного неба</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Disegnando un cuore con le dita verso il cielo stellato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dui xing kong zhi jian hua chu le xin xing</span></p>
      <p begin="00:58.000" end="01:01.270" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:58.000" end="00:58.220">星</span><span begin="00:58.250" end="00:58.370">际</span><span begin="00:58.470" end="00:58.690">闪</span><span begin="00:58.690" end="00:58.830">耀</span><span begin="00:58.910" end="00:59.350">光</span><span begin="00:59.350" end="00:59.720">影</span><span begin="00:59.770" end="00:59.970">落</span><span begin="00:59.970" end="01:00.100">入</span><span begin="01:00.170" end="01:00.370">你</span><span begin="01:00.370" end="01:00.560">的</span><span begin="01:00.560" end="01:00.950">眼</span><span begin="01:00.980" end="01:01.270">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際閃耀光影落入你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar shining light and shadows fall into your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の瞬く光と影が君の瞳に舞い落ちる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리의 반짝이는 빛이 네 눈동자에 내려앉아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'éclat scintillant des astres tombe dans tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La luz y sombra estelar brillan y caen en tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten fallen strahlend in deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O brilho cintilante do espaço cai nos seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцающий свет звезд падает в твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Luci e ombre brillanti delle stelle cadono nei tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji shan yao guang ying luo ru ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:01.630" end="01:04.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:01.630" end="01:01.800">如</span><span begin="01:01.850" end="01:02.050">迷</span><span begin="01:02.050" end="01:02.150">人</span><span begin="01:02.260" end="01:02.330">的</span><span begin="01:02.420" end="01:02.570">水</span><span begin="01:02.650" end="01:03.110">晶</span><span begin="01:03.110" end="01:03.190">把</span><span begin="01:03.340" end="01:03.620">浪</span><span begin="01:03.700" end="01:03.790">漫</span><span begin="01:03.900" end="01:04.310">放</span><span begin="01:04.310" end="01:04.710">映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如迷人的水晶把浪漫放映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like charming crystals projecting romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">魅惑的な水晶のようにロマンチックを映し出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">매혹적인 수정처럼 로맨스를 비춰주네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un cristal envoûtant projetant la romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un cristal encantador proyectando el romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und projizieren Romantik wie ein bezaubernder Kristall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Projetando o romance como um cristal encantador</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно чарующий кристалл транслирующий романтику</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un cristallo incantevole che proietta il romanticismo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ru mi ren de shui jing ba lang man fang ying</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.110" end="01:08.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:05.110" end="01:05.280">爱</span><span begin="01:05.340" end="01:05.500">是</span><span begin="01:05.560" end="01:05.790">种</span><span begin="01:05.790" end="01:05.870">魔</span><span begin="01:05.970" end="01:06.320">法</span><span begin="01:06.420" end="01:06.860">给</span><span begin="01:06.860" end="01:07.190">我</span><span begin="01:07.250" end="01:07.410">们</span><span begin="01:07.480" end="01:07.790">指</span><span begin="01:07.900" end="01:08.080">引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛是種魔法給我們指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love is a kind of magic guiding us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">愛は魔法のように私たちを導いてくれる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑은 우리를 이끌어주는 마법이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'amour est une magie qui nous guide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El amor es una magia que nos guía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe ist eine Magie die uns leitet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O amor é uma magia que nos serve de guia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Любовь это магия что указывает нам путь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L'amore è una magia che ci fa da guida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ai shi zhong mo fa gei wo men zhi yin</span></p>
      <p begin="01:08.470" end="01:11.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:08.470" end="01:08.720">穿</span><span begin="01:08.720" end="01:08.840">过</span><span begin="01:08.890" end="01:09.100">黑</span><span begin="01:09.100" end="01:09.210">暗</span><span begin="01:09.280" end="01:09.550">森</span><span begin="01:09.550" end="01:09.720">林</span><span begin="01:09.960" end="01:10.300">去</span><span begin="01:10.360" end="01:10.510">寻</span><span begin="01:10.560" end="01:10.740">找</span><span begin="01:10.770" end="01:10.860">黎</span><span begin="01:10.990" end="01:11.350">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">穿過黑暗森林去尋找黎明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Through the dark forest to seek the dawn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">暗い森を抜けて夜明けを探しに行こう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어두운 숲을 지나 여명을 찾아가게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À travers la sombre forêt à la recherche de l'aube</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atravesando el bosque oscuro para buscar el amanecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Durch den dunklen Wald um die Morgendämmerung zu finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Atravessando a floresta escura em busca do amanhecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сквозь темный лес на поиски рассвета</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraversando la foresta oscura per cercare l'alba</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">chuan guo hei an sen lin qu xun zhao li ming</span></p>
      <p begin="01:11.370" end="01:14.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:11.370" end="01:11.560">星</span><span begin="01:11.610" end="01:11.700">际</span><span begin="01:11.770" end="01:12.000">洒</span><span begin="01:12.030" end="01:12.150">下</span><span begin="01:12.250" end="01:12.670">光</span><span begin="01:12.670" end="01:13.020">影</span><span begin="01:13.080" end="01:13.280">点</span><span begin="01:13.320" end="01:13.470">亮</span><span begin="01:13.510" end="01:13.670">你</span><span begin="01:13.700" end="01:13.890">的</span><span begin="01:13.890" end="01:14.280">眼</span><span begin="01:14.280" end="01:14.560">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際灑下光影點亮你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar sprinkled light and shadows light up your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の光と影が降り注ぎ君の瞳を照らし出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리가 흩뿌린 빛이 네 눈동자를 밝히고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La lueur des astres se répand et illumine tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El espacio esparce luz y sombra iluminando tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten regnen herab und erhellen deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O universo derrama luz iluminando os seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Звездный свет проливается зажигая твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le stelle spargono luci e ombre illuminando i tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji sa xia guang ying dian liang ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:14.910" end="01:18.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:14.910" end="01:15.100">像</span><span begin="01:15.160" end="01:15.280">缤</span><span begin="01:15.350" end="01:15.580">纷</span><span begin="01:15.580" end="01:15.730">的</span><span begin="01:15.790" end="01:15.910">梦</span><span begin="01:15.980" end="01:16.430">境</span><span begin="01:16.430" end="01:16.560">我</span><span begin="01:16.660" end="01:17.040">不</span><span begin="01:17.040" end="01:17.140">愿</span><span begin="01:17.240" end="01:17.540">苏</span><span begin="01:17.660" end="01:18.000">醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">像繽紛的夢境我不願甦醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like a colorful dreamland from which I don't want to wake up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">色彩豊かな夢のようで私は目覚めたくない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다채로운 꿈결 같아 난 깨어나고 싶지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un rêve coloré dont je refuse d'être éveillée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un sueño colorido del que no quiero despertar maravillada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie ein farbenfroher Traum aus dem ich nicht erwachen will</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como em um sonho colorido do qual eu, apaixonada, não quero acordar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно в красочном сне от которого я не хотела бы просыпаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come in un sogno colorato da cui non voglio essere svegliata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang bin fen de meng jing wo bu yuan su xing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:18.520" end="01:21.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:18.520" end="01:18.620">余</span><span begin="01:18.690" end="01:18.930">生</span><span begin="01:18.930" end="01:19.040">的</span><span begin="01:19.120" end="01:19.330">光</span><span begin="01:19.330" end="01:19.600">阴</span><span begin="01:19.730" end="01:20.170">牵</span><span begin="01:20.170" end="01:20.470">你</span><span begin="01:20.540" end="01:20.710">手</span><span begin="01:20.790" end="01:21.070">前</span><span begin="01:21.200" end="01:21.400">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">餘生的光陰牽你手前行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Holding your hand to move forward for the rest of my life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">残りの人生の時間は君と手を繋いで歩んでいく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">남은 생의 시간 동안 네 손을 잡고 나아갈게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je marcherai en te tenant la main pour le reste de ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El tiempo del resto de mi vida avanzaré aferrada a tu mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Rest meines Lebens werde ich deine Hand haltend voranschreiten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No tempo que me resta caminharei segurando a sua mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Остаток жизни я пройду держа тебя за руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per il resto del tempo camminerò tenendoti per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yu sheng de guang yin qian ni shou qian xing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:21.640" end="01:26.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:21.640" end="01:21.760">我</span><span begin="01:21.850" end="01:22.190">们</span><span begin="01:22.230" end="01:22.370">共</span><span begin="01:22.460" end="01:22.680">赴</span><span begin="01:22.680" end="01:22.760">一</span><span begin="01:22.880" end="01:23.160">场</span><span begin="01:23.480" end="01:23.930">光</span><span begin="01:23.930" end="01:24.080">年</span><span begin="01:24.190" end="01:24.770">的</span><span begin="01:24.770" end="01:25.380">旅</span><span begin="01:25.590" end="01:26.410">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們共赴一場光年的旅行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let's go on a light-year journey together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちは共に光年の旅へと出かけるんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 함께 광년의 여행을 떠나자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Partons ensemble pour un voyage d'une année-lumière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Juntos emprendemos un viaje de años luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir begeben uns gemeinsam auf eine lichtjahrelange Reise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos embarcar juntos em uma viagem de anos-luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы вместе отправимся в путешествие длиною в световой год</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Siamo pronte a partire per un viaggio lungo anni luce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo men gong fu yi chang guang nian de lv xing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:39.060" end="01:43.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:39.060" end="01:39.160">你</span><span begin="01:39.290" end="01:39.650">就</span><span begin="01:39.750" end="01:40.060">像</span><span begin="01:40.060" end="01:40.430">夜</span><span begin="01:40.660" end="01:41.040">色</span><span begin="01:41.800" end="01:42.620">温</span><span begin="01:42.620" end="01:42.790">柔</span><span begin="01:42.940" end="01:43.270">降</span><span begin="01:43.330" end="01:43.810">临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你就像夜色溫柔降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You gently descend just like the night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君はまるで優しく降り注ぐ夜のよう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 밤의 어둠처럼 다정하게 내려앉아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu descends avec la même douceur que la nuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desciendes suavemente como la misma noche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du brichst herein so sanft wie die Nacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você chega tão gentilmente quanto a própria noite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты нежно спускаешься словно ночная мгла</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei come la notte che scende dolcemente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ni jiu xiang ye se wen rou jiang lin</span></p>
      <p begin="01:45.740" end="01:50.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:45.740" end="01:45.820">这</span><span begin="01:45.930" end="01:46.340">城</span><span begin="01:46.380" end="01:46.550">市</span><span begin="01:46.710" end="01:47.080">和</span><span begin="01:47.310" end="01:47.670">你</span><span begin="01:48.490" end="01:49.090">都</span><span begin="01:49.310" end="01:49.560">很</span><span begin="01:49.560" end="01:49.940">安</span><span begin="01:50.150" end="01:50.940">静</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這城市和你都很安靜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Both this city and you are so quiet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この街も君もとても静かだね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 도시도 너도 아주 고요해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette ville et toi êtes si paisibles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esta ciudad y tú están muy silenciosos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese Stadt und du ihr seid beide so still</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta cidade e você estão tão tranquilos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И этот город и ты так безмятежны</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questa città e tu siete così silenziose</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">zhe cheng shi he ni dou hen an jing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:52.670" end="01:57.510" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:52.670" end="01:52.820">慢</span><span begin="01:52.880" end="01:52.970">慢</span><span begin="01:53.050" end="01:53.440">穿</span><span begin="01:53.490" end="01:53.850">过</span><span begin="01:53.970" end="01:54.190">缤</span><span begin="01:54.280" end="01:54.740">纷</span><span begin="01:54.740" end="01:54.960">的</span><span begin="01:55.100" end="01:56.780">街</span><span begin="01:56.960" end="01:57.510">景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">慢慢穿過繽紛的街景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Slowly passing through the colorful street scenes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">色彩豊かな街並みをゆっくりと通り抜ける</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">알록달록한 거리 풍경을 천천히 지나가면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Traversant lentement les rues aux couleurs éclatantes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atravesando lentamente el colorido paisaje de las calles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Langsam durchqueren wir die bunten Straßen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Atravessando lentamente a paisagem colorida das ruas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Медленно проходя сквозь пестрые уличные пейзажи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraversando lentamente le scene colorate delle strade</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">man man chuan guo bin fen de jie jing</span></p>
      <p begin="01:58.030" end="02:02.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:58.030" end="01:58.240">小</span><span begin="01:58.270" end="01:58.460">小</span><span begin="01:58.490" end="01:58.700">的</span><span begin="01:58.860" end="01:59.040">幸</span><span begin="01:59.150" end="01:59.630">福</span><span begin="02:00.170" end="02:00.590">也</span><span begin="02:00.590" end="02:00.800">一</span><span begin="02:00.840" end="02:01.040">路</span><span begin="02:01.190" end="02:01.620">随</span><span begin="02:01.780" end="02:02.570">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">小小的幸福也一路隨行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Little happiness also follows along the way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ささやかな幸せもずっと付いてくる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">자그마한 행복도 이 길을 따라오네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un petit bonheur nous accompagne tout au long du chemin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una pequeña felicidad también nos acompaña en el camino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein kleines bisschen Glück begleitet uns auf Schritt und Tritt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Uma pequena felicidade me acompanha, encantada com o caminho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И маленькое счастье следует за нами всю дорогу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Accompagnate da una piccola felicità lungo il cammino</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiao xiao de xing fu ye yi lu sui xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:05.380" end="02:08.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:05.380" end="02:05.470">看</span><span begin="02:05.560" end="02:05.670">天</span><span begin="02:05.780" end="02:05.870">台</span><span begin="02:05.960" end="02:06.420">上</span><span begin="02:06.420" end="02:06.510">路</span><span begin="02:06.620" end="02:06.920">过</span><span begin="02:07.020" end="02:07.110">几</span><span begin="02:07.220" end="02:07.390">颗</span><span begin="02:07.410" end="02:07.510">流</span><span begin="02:07.630" end="02:08.110">星</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看天台上路過幾顆流星</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Watching a few shooting stars pass by over the rooftop</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">屋上を通り過ぎる幾つかの流れ星を見て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">옥상 위를 스쳐 지나가는 별똥별들을 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Regarde ces étoiles filantes passer au-dessus du toit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Viendo pasar unas estrellas fugaces desde la azotea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieh wie ein paar Sternschnuppen über die Dachterrasse ziehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Olho para as estrelas cadentes passando pelo terraço</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотрю с крыши на пролетающие падающие звезды</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guarda qualche stella cadente passare sopra la terrazza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">kan tian tai shang lu guo ji ke liu xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:08.700" end="02:11.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:08.700" end="02:08.770">说</span><span begin="02:08.870" end="02:09.020">出</span><span begin="02:09.110" end="02:09.340">口</span><span begin="02:09.340" end="02:09.560">的</span><span begin="02:09.690" end="02:09.980">誓</span><span begin="02:09.980" end="02:10.320">言</span><span begin="02:10.400" end="02:10.580">会</span><span begin="02:10.580" end="02:10.700">有</span><span begin="02:10.820" end="02:11.020">回</span><span begin="02:11.020" end="02:11.560">音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">說出口的誓言會有回音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The vows spoken out loud will have an echo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">口にした誓いは必ず響き合う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입 밖으로 꺼낸 맹세는 메아리가 되어 돌아올 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les vœux prononcés trouveront toujours un écho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las promesas pronunciadas tendrán su eco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ausgesprochene Schwüre werden ein Echo finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As promessas ditas em voz alta terão um eco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Произнесенные клятвы обязательно отзовутся эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le promesse pronunciate avranno un'eco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">shuo chu kou de shi yan hui you hui yin</span></p>
      <p begin="02:12.030" end="02:14.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:12.030" end="02:12.110">那</span><span begin="02:12.220" end="02:12.480">就</span><span begin="02:12.480" end="02:12.760">让</span><span begin="02:12.760" end="02:12.890">我</span><span begin="02:12.940" end="02:13.170">们</span><span begin="02:13.520" end="02:13.740">勇</span><span begin="02:13.740" end="02:13.850">敢</span><span begin="02:13.950" end="02:14.170">地</span><span begin="02:14.170" end="02:14.510">约</span><span begin="02:14.560" end="02:14.710">定</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那就讓我們勇敢地約定</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Then let us bravely make a promise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから勇敢に約束を交わそう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼 우리 용기 내어 약속하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors faisons courageusement notre promesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Entonces hagamos valientemente una promesa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also lass uns mutig unser Versprechen geben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então vamos fazer a nossa promessa corajosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так давай же смело дадим друг другу обещание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Allora promettiamocelo coraggiosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na jiu rang wo men yong gan de yue ding</span></p>
      <p begin="02:14.740" end="02:17.630" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:14.740" end="02:14.890">对</span><span begin="02:14.930" end="02:15.140">星</span><span begin="02:15.140" end="02:15.350">空</span><span begin="02:15.390" end="02:15.520">指</span><span begin="02:15.570" end="02:15.720">尖</span><span begin="02:15.800" end="02:15.880">画</span><span begin="02:15.990" end="02:16.380">出</span><span begin="02:16.440" end="02:16.520">了</span><span begin="02:16.650" end="02:16.900">心</span><span begin="02:17.070" end="02:17.630">形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對星空指尖畫出了心形</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing a heart shape at the starry sky with our fingertips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星空に向かって指先でハートを描く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별 쏟아지는 하늘에 손끝으로 하트를 그리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dessinant un cœur du bout des doigts vers le ciel étoilé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dibujando un corazón con la punta de los dedos hacia el firmamento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und mit den Fingerspitzen ein Herz in den Sternenhimmel zeichnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desenhando um coração com a ponta dos dedos para o céu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рисуя пальцами сердце на фоне звездного неба</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Disegnando un cuore con le dita verso il cielo stellato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">dui xing kong zhi jian hua chu le xin xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:18.040" end="02:21.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:18.040" end="02:18.240">星</span><span begin="02:18.240" end="02:18.360">际</span><span begin="02:18.470" end="02:18.680">闪</span><span begin="02:18.680" end="02:18.820">耀</span><span begin="02:18.920" end="02:19.350">光</span><span begin="02:19.350" end="02:19.710">影</span><span begin="02:19.770" end="02:19.960">落</span><span begin="02:19.960" end="02:20.080">入</span><span begin="02:20.160" end="02:20.360">你</span><span begin="02:20.360" end="02:20.550">的</span><span begin="02:20.550" end="02:20.940">眼</span><span begin="02:20.970" end="02:21.230">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際閃耀光影落入你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar shining light and shadows fall into your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の瞬く光と影が君の瞳に舞い落ちる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리의 반짝이는 빛이 네 눈동자에 내려앉아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'éclat scintillant des astres tombe dans tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La luz y sombra estelar brillan y caen en tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten fallen strahlend in deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O brilho cintilante do espaço cai nos seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцающий свет звезд падает в твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Luci e ombre brillanti delle stelle cadono nei tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji shan yao guang ying luo ru ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:21.620" end="02:24.650" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:21.620" end="02:21.780">如</span><span begin="02:21.850" end="02:22.040">迷</span><span begin="02:22.040" end="02:22.160">人</span><span begin="02:22.240" end="02:22.320">的</span><span begin="02:22.400" end="02:22.630">水</span><span begin="02:22.630" end="02:23.090">晶</span><span begin="02:23.090" end="02:23.190">把</span><span begin="02:23.330" end="02:23.600">浪</span><span begin="02:23.690" end="02:23.790">漫</span><span begin="02:23.880" end="02:24.280">放</span><span begin="02:24.280" end="02:24.650">映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如迷人的水晶把浪漫放映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like charming crystals projecting romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">魅惑的な水晶のようにロマンチックを映し出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">매혹적인 수정처럼 로맨스를 비춰주네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un cristal envoûtant projetant la romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un cristal encantador proyectando el romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und projizieren Romantik wie ein bezaubernder Kristall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Projetando o romance como um cristal encantador</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно чарующий кристалл транслирующий романтику</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un cristallo incantevole che proietta il romanticismo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ru mi ren de shui jing ba lang man fang ying</span></p>
      <p begin="02:25.120" end="02:28.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:25.120" end="02:25.270">爱</span><span begin="02:25.350" end="02:25.510">是</span><span begin="02:25.570" end="02:25.790">种</span><span begin="02:25.790" end="02:25.860">魔</span><span begin="02:25.980" end="02:26.330">法</span><span begin="02:26.410" end="02:26.740">给</span><span begin="02:26.870" end="02:27.170">我</span><span begin="02:27.230" end="02:27.330">们</span><span begin="02:27.480" end="02:27.770">指</span><span begin="02:27.890" end="02:28.080">引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛是種魔法給我們指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love is a kind of magic guiding us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">愛は魔法のように私たちを導いてくれる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑은 우리를 이끌어주는 마법이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'amour est une magie qui nous guide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El amor es una magia que nos guía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe ist eine Magie die uns leitet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O amor é uma magia que nos serve de guia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Любовь это магия что указывает нам путь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L'amore è una magia che ci fa da guida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ai shi zhong mo fa gei wo men zhi yin</span></p>
      <p begin="02:28.460" end="02:31.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:28.460" end="02:28.720">穿</span><span begin="02:28.720" end="02:28.820">过</span><span begin="02:28.900" end="02:29.070">黑</span><span begin="02:29.070" end="02:29.170">暗</span><span begin="02:29.270" end="02:29.540">森</span><span begin="02:29.540" end="02:29.690">林</span><span begin="02:29.950" end="02:30.300">去</span><span begin="02:30.350" end="02:30.500">寻</span><span begin="02:30.550" end="02:30.760">找</span><span begin="02:30.760" end="02:30.860">黎</span><span begin="02:31.000" end="02:31.440">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">穿過黑暗森林去尋找黎明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Through the dark forest to seek the dawn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">暗い森を抜けて夜明けを探しに行こう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어두운 숲을 지나 여명을 찾아가게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À travers la sombre forêt à la recherche de l'aube</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atravesando el bosque oscuro para buscar el amanecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Durch den dunklen Wald um die Morgendämmerung zu finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Atravessando a floresta escura em busca do amanhecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сквозь темный лес на поиски рассвета</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraversando la foresta oscura per cercare l'alba</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">chuan guo hei an sen lin qu xun zhao li ming</span></p>
      <p begin="02:31.370" end="02:34.580" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:31.370" end="02:31.610">星</span><span begin="02:31.610" end="02:31.710">际</span><span begin="02:31.770" end="02:31.980">洒</span><span begin="02:32.030" end="02:32.150">下</span><span begin="02:32.260" end="02:32.670">光</span><span begin="02:32.670" end="02:33.010">影</span><span begin="02:33.080" end="02:33.320">点</span><span begin="02:33.320" end="02:33.510">亮</span><span begin="02:33.510" end="02:33.670">你</span><span begin="02:33.700" end="02:33.890">的</span><span begin="02:33.890" end="02:34.270">眼</span><span begin="02:34.310" end="02:34.580">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際灑下光影點亮你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar sprinkled light and shadows light up your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の光と影が降り注ぎ君の瞳を照らし出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리가 흩뿌린 빛이 네 눈동자를 밝히고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La lueur des astres se répand et illumine tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El espacio esparce luz y sombra iluminando tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten regnen herab und erhellen deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O universo derrama luz iluminando os seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Звездный свет проливается зажигая твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le stelle spargono luci e ombre illuminando i tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji sa xia guang ying dian liang ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:34.920" end="02:38.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:34.920" end="02:35.110">像</span><span begin="02:35.170" end="02:35.280">缤</span><span begin="02:35.360" end="02:35.580">纷</span><span begin="02:35.580" end="02:35.740">的</span><span begin="02:35.800" end="02:35.880">梦</span><span begin="02:35.990" end="02:36.430">境</span><span begin="02:36.430" end="02:36.560">我</span><span begin="02:36.660" end="02:37.050">不</span><span begin="02:37.050" end="02:37.150">愿</span><span begin="02:37.250" end="02:37.540">苏</span><span begin="02:37.670" end="02:38.000">醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">像繽紛的夢境我不願甦醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like a colorful dreamland from which I don't want to wake up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">色彩豊かな夢のようで私は目覚めたくない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다채로운 꿈결 같아 난 깨어나고 싶지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un rêve coloré dont je refuse d'être éveillée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un sueño colorido del que no quiero despertar maravillada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie ein farbenfroher Traum aus dem ich nicht erwachen will</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como em um sonho colorido do qual eu, apaixonada, não quero acordar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно в красочном сне от которого я не хотела бы просыпаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come in un sogno colorato da cui non voglio essere svegliata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang bin fen de meng jing wo bu yuan su xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.500" end="02:41.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:38.500" end="02:38.590">余</span><span begin="02:38.680" end="02:38.870">生</span><span begin="02:38.910" end="02:39.010">的</span><span begin="02:39.110" end="02:39.350">光</span><span begin="02:39.350" end="02:39.610">阴</span><span begin="02:39.740" end="02:40.180">牵</span><span begin="02:40.180" end="02:40.470">你</span><span begin="02:40.540" end="02:40.720">手</span><span begin="02:40.790" end="02:41.090">前</span><span begin="02:41.210" end="02:41.380">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">餘生的光陰牽你手前行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Holding your hand to move forward for the rest of my life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">残りの人生の時間は君と手を繋いで歩んでいく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">남은 생의 시간 동안 네 손을 잡고 나아갈게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je marcherai en te tenant la main pour le reste de ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El tiempo del resto de mi vida avanzaré aferrada a tu mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Rest meines Lebens werde ich deine Hand haltend voranschreiten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No tempo que me resta caminharei segurando a sua mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Остаток жизни я пройду держа тебя за руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per il resto del tempo camminerò tenendoti per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yu sheng de guang yin qian ni shou qian xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:41.640" end="02:47.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:41.640" end="02:41.740">我</span><span begin="02:41.830" end="02:42.250">们</span><span begin="02:42.250" end="02:42.360">共</span><span begin="02:42.460" end="02:42.680">赴</span><span begin="02:42.680" end="02:42.760">一</span><span begin="02:42.860" end="02:43.150">场</span><span begin="02:43.520" end="02:43.970">光</span><span begin="02:43.970" end="02:44.110">年</span><span begin="02:44.260" end="02:44.640">的</span><span begin="02:45.210" end="02:45.800">旅</span><span begin="02:46.050" end="02:47.350">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們共赴一場光年的旅行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let's go on a light-year journey together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちは共に光年の旅へと出かけるんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 함께 광년의 여행을 떠나자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Partons ensemble pour un voyage d'une année-lumière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Juntos emprendemos un viaje de años luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir begeben uns gemeinsam auf eine lichtjahrelange Reise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos embarcar juntos em uma viagem de anos-luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы вместе отправимся в путешествие длиною в световой год</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Siamo pronte a partire per un viaggio lungo anni luce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo men gong fu yi chang guang nian de lv xing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.060" end="02:51.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:48.060" end="02:48.310">星</span><span begin="02:48.310" end="02:48.420">际</span><span begin="02:48.530" end="02:48.750">闪</span><span begin="02:48.750" end="02:48.850">耀</span><span begin="02:48.950" end="02:49.330">光</span><span begin="02:49.330" end="02:49.720">影</span><span begin="02:49.770" end="02:50.000">落</span><span begin="02:50.000" end="02:50.100">入</span><span begin="02:50.190" end="02:50.350">你</span><span begin="02:50.380" end="02:50.520">的</span><span begin="02:50.610" end="02:50.980">眼</span><span begin="02:51.030" end="02:51.280">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際閃耀光影落入你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar shining light and shadows fall into your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の瞬く光と影が君の瞳に舞い落ちる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리의 반짝이는 빛이 네 눈동자에 내려앉아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'éclat scintillant des astres tombe dans tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La luz y sombra estelar brillan y caen en tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten fallen strahlend in deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O brilho cintilante do espaço cai nos seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мерцающий свет звезд падает в твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Luci e ombre brillanti delle stelle cadono nei tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji shan yao guang ying luo ru ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="02:51.680" end="02:54.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:51.680" end="02:51.800">如</span><span begin="02:51.880" end="02:52.080">迷</span><span begin="02:52.080" end="02:52.180">人</span><span begin="02:52.290" end="02:52.380">的</span><span begin="02:52.450" end="02:52.590">水</span><span begin="02:52.700" end="02:53.110">晶</span><span begin="02:53.110" end="02:53.200">把</span><span begin="02:53.370" end="02:53.610">浪</span><span begin="02:53.740" end="02:53.800">漫</span><span begin="02:53.920" end="02:54.320">放</span><span begin="02:54.320" end="02:54.760">映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如迷人的水晶把浪漫放映</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like charming crystals projecting romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">魅惑的な水晶のようにロマンチックを映し出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">매혹적인 수정처럼 로맨스를 비춰주네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un cristal envoûtant projetant la romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un cristal encantador proyectando el romance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und projizieren Romantik wie ein bezaubernder Kristall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Projetando o romance como um cristal encantador</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно чарующий кристалл транслирующий романтику</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un cristallo incantevole che proietta il romanticismo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ru mi ren de shui jing ba lang man fang ying</span></p>
      <p begin="02:55.190" end="02:58.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:55.190" end="02:55.270">爱</span><span begin="02:55.380" end="02:55.480">是</span><span begin="02:55.560" end="02:55.790">种</span><span begin="02:55.790" end="02:55.880">魔</span><span begin="02:55.990" end="02:56.270">法</span><span begin="02:56.430" end="02:56.760">给</span><span begin="02:56.820" end="02:57.180">我</span><span begin="02:57.260" end="02:57.370">们</span><span begin="02:57.510" end="02:57.870">指</span><span begin="02:57.870" end="02:58.060">引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">愛是種魔法給我們指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Love is a kind of magic guiding us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">愛は魔法のように私たちを導いてくれる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑은 우리를 이끌어주는 마법이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L'amour est une magie qui nous guide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El amor es una magia que nos guía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe ist eine Magie die uns leitet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O amor é uma magia que nos serve de guia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Любовь это магия что указывает нам путь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L'amore è una magia che ci fa da guida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ai shi zhong mo fa gei wo men zhi yin</span></p>
      <p begin="02:58.440" end="03:01.420" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="02:58.440" end="02:58.690">穿</span><span begin="02:58.690" end="02:58.820">过</span><span begin="02:58.890" end="02:59.070">黑</span><span begin="02:59.070" end="02:59.170">暗</span><span begin="02:59.280" end="02:59.610">森</span><span begin="02:59.610" end="02:59.850">林</span><span begin="02:59.940" end="03:00.300">去</span><span begin="03:00.350" end="03:00.510">寻</span><span begin="03:00.550" end="03:00.790">找</span><span begin="03:00.790" end="03:00.890">黎</span><span begin="03:01.000" end="03:01.420">明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">穿過黑暗森林去尋找黎明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Through the dark forest to seek the dawn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">暗い森を抜けて夜明けを探しに行こう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어두운 숲을 지나 여명을 찾아가게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À travers la sombre forêt à la recherche de l'aube</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atravesando el bosque oscuro para buscar el amanecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Durch den dunklen Wald um die Morgendämmerung zu finden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Atravessando a floresta escura em busca do amanhecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сквозь темный лес на поиски рассвета</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Attraversando la foresta oscura per cercare l'alba</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">chuan guo hei an sen lin qu xun zhao li ming</span></p>
      <p begin="03:01.370" end="03:04.580" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:01.370" end="03:01.610">星</span><span begin="03:01.610" end="03:01.710">际</span><span begin="03:01.790" end="03:02.000">洒</span><span begin="03:02.030" end="03:02.130">下</span><span begin="03:02.250" end="03:02.670">光</span><span begin="03:02.670" end="03:03.030">影</span><span begin="03:03.070" end="03:03.320">点</span><span begin="03:03.320" end="03:03.480">亮</span><span begin="03:03.520" end="03:03.700">你</span><span begin="03:03.700" end="03:03.890">的</span><span begin="03:03.890" end="03:04.280">眼</span><span begin="03:04.310" end="03:04.580">睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">星際灑下光影點亮你的眼睛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Interstellar sprinkled light and shadows light up your eyes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々の光と影が降り注ぎ君の瞳を照らし出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별무리가 흩뿌린 빛이 네 눈동자를 밝히고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La lueur des astres se répand et illumine tes yeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El espacio esparce luz y sombra iluminando tus ojos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sternenlicht und Schatten regnen herab und erhellen deine Augen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O universo derrama luz iluminando os seus olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Звездный свет проливается зажигая твои глаза</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le stelle spargono luci e ombre illuminando i tuoi occhi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xing ji sa xia guang ying dian liang ni de yan jing</span></p>
      <p begin="03:04.930" end="03:08.010" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:04.930" end="03:05.090">像</span><span begin="03:05.160" end="03:05.300">缤</span><span begin="03:05.370" end="03:05.600">纷</span><span begin="03:05.600" end="03:05.750">的</span><span begin="03:05.780" end="03:05.930">梦</span><span begin="03:05.990" end="03:06.430">境</span><span begin="03:06.430" end="03:06.500">我</span><span begin="03:06.670" end="03:07.010">不</span><span begin="03:07.010" end="03:07.110">愿</span><span begin="03:07.230" end="03:07.520">苏</span><span begin="03:07.650" end="03:08.010">醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">像繽紛的夢境我不願甦醒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like a colorful dreamland from which I don't want to wake up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">色彩豊かな夢のようで私は目覚めたくない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다채로운 꿈결 같아 난 깨어나고 싶지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme un rêve coloré dont je refuse d'être éveillée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como un sueño colorido del que no quiero despertar maravillada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie ein farbenfroher Traum aus dem ich nicht erwachen will</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como em um sonho colorido do qual eu, apaixonada, não quero acordar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно в красочном сне от которого я не хотела бы просыпаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come in un sogno colorato da cui non voglio essere svegliata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">xiang bin fen de meng jing wo bu yuan su xing</span></p>
      <p begin="03:08.470" end="03:11.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:08.470" end="03:08.600">余</span><span begin="03:08.680" end="03:08.920">生</span><span begin="03:08.920" end="03:09.010">的</span><span begin="03:09.090" end="03:09.340">光</span><span begin="03:09.340" end="03:09.640">阴</span><span begin="03:09.720" end="03:10.140">牵</span><span begin="03:10.140" end="03:10.470">你</span><span begin="03:10.530" end="03:10.660">手</span><span begin="03:10.790" end="03:11.040">前</span><span begin="03:11.180" end="03:11.360">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">餘生的光陰牽你手前行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Holding your hand to move forward for the rest of my life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">残りの人生の時間は君と手を繋いで歩んでいく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">남은 생의 시간 동안 네 손을 잡고 나아갈게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je marcherai en te tenant la main pour le reste de ma vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El tiempo del resto de mi vida avanzaré aferrada a tu mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den Rest meines Lebens werde ich deine Hand haltend voranschreiten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No tempo que me resta caminharei segurando a sua mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Остаток жизни я пройду держа тебя за руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per il resto del tempo camminerò tenendoti per mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yu sheng de guang yin qian ni shou qian xing</span></p>
      <p begin="03:11.640" end="03:17.550" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:11.640" end="03:11.750">我</span><span begin="03:11.850" end="03:12.240">们</span><span begin="03:12.240" end="03:12.360">共</span><span begin="03:12.460" end="03:12.680">赴</span><span begin="03:12.680" end="03:12.760">一</span><span begin="03:12.860" end="03:13.160">场</span><span begin="03:13.500" end="03:13.950">光</span><span begin="03:13.950" end="03:14.090">年</span><span begin="03:14.240" end="03:14.640">的</span><span begin="03:15.240" end="03:15.800">旅</span><span begin="03:16.070" end="03:17.550">行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們共赴一場光年的旅行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let's go on a light-year journey together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちは共に光年の旅へと出かけるんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 함께 광년의 여행을 떠나자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Partons ensemble pour un voyage d'une année-lumière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Juntos emprendemos un viaje de años luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir begeben uns gemeinsam auf eine lichtjahrelange Reise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos embarcar juntos em uma viagem de anos-luz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы вместе отправимся в путешествие длиною в световой год</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Siamo pronte a partire per un viaggio lungo anni luce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">wo men gong fu yi chang guang nian de lv xing</span></p>
